<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I would have to disagree with most people here. I found the 4 - 5 book extremely boring, and the 6 one bearable. However, this book is really good. It<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I would have to disagree with most people here. I found the 4 - 5 book extremely boring, and the 6 one bearable. However, this book is really good. It's not as good as the first two books, but reminds me of 3 one if that helps. Anyway, keep reading you won't be disappointed.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
